short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fix the default user id of Google Calendar Meet links when you have calendars from multiple email accounts.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
CHANGELOG
https://github.com/metaist/fix-gcal-meet/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md

DESCRIPTION
Do you get the "Ask to Join" button in Google Meet because you opened the link from a shared Google Calendar? This extension tries to fix the Google Meet links to reduce the number of times you have to click "Switch account".
